""><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><b style="font-family:Poppins;font-size:x-large;"><strong>9.Megami no Café Terrace</strong></b></span></div><div><div><div class="separator" style="clear:both;text-align:center;"><a style="margin-left:1em;margin-right:1em;" href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgUTstqKUVHHXnYYeJgWJd0_Gb_6qTYBI-rR8paIvZK5O8CRRPc1DPl6EotYkmE8Wq_923kRQ9vFUnF3G98Lph7Q8p-0zgN-mPJdyhqcQdq3EuaXBrQDZj7_jKYeiFqTglZrgkDJ5eX435JS3X1TXbpYNHuaYO2xg7l5CdtDV-94zqguR3DNWLY7LrLvA/s2688/mv1.png"><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><img src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgUTstqKUVHHXnYYeJgWJd0_Gb_6qTYBI-rR8paIvZK5O8CRRPc1DPl6EotYkmE8Wq_923kRQ9vFUnF3G98Lph7Q8p-0zgN-mPJdyhqcQdq3EuaXBrQDZj7_jKYeiFqTglZrgkDJ5eX435JS3X1TXbpYNHuaYO2xg7l5CdtDV-94zqguR3DNWLY7LrLvA/s320/mv1.png" border="0" data-original-height="2688" data-original-width="1920" height="320" width="229"></span></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear:both;text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:Nunito;font-size:xx-small;">Goddess Café Terrace</span></div><div><div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><strong>Judul Alternatif&nbsp; :&nbsp;</strong>Goddess Café Terrace</span></div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><strong>Rilis&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp;</strong>April 2023 [Spring 2023]</span></div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><strong>Studio :&nbsp;</strong>Tezuka Productions</span></div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><strong>Genre&nbsp; :&nbsp;</strong>Fantasy, Supernatural</span></div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><strong>Site&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;:&nbsp; </strong></span><a href="https://goddess-cafe.com/"><span style="font-family:Nunito;">goddess-cafe.com</span></a></div></div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div></div></div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;">Nge-harem di rumah nenek</span></div><div><br>&nbsp;</div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;"><strong>Sinopsis:</strong></span></div><div><br>&nbsp;</div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;">Setelah mendengar kabar kematian neneknya,<strong>Kasukabe Hayato</strong>&nbsp;kembali ke rumah masa kecilnya.Sudah 3 tahun semenjak ia pergi,saat kembali tempat itu sudah menjadi tempat penampungan.Mereka adalah Lima gadis yang menjadi pelayan di kafe-tua-milik neneknya.Setelah semua fakta terkumpul,pilihan Hayato dua.Merobohkan rumah tua itu.Atau melanjutkan bisnis bersama "dewi-dewi" yang ditinggalkan oleh neneknya.</span></div><div><br>&nbsp;</div><div><span style="font-family:Nunito;">Itu dia beberapa rekomendasi anime romance seru yang rilis di musim semi 2023.Sekian pembahasan kali ini.Makasih Udah mampir.Bye&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div></div></div><div style="font-family:;" times="" new="">&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div><div style="font-family:;" times="" new="">&nbsp;</div></div><div style="font-family:;" times="" new="">&nbsp;</div></div></div><div><div>&nbsp;</div></div></div></div>